00:15:26.634 --> 00:15:27.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¡Comandante!

147
00:15:28.886 --> 00:15:29.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Qué...

148
00:15:30.638 --> 00:15:31.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
