00:22:38.732 --> 00:22:39.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Tengo...?

209
00:22:40.442 --> 00:22:42.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Tengo derecho a la vida?

210
00:22:53.580 --> 00:22:55.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No puedes borrar el pasado.

211
00:23:02.047 --> 00:23:02.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Pero...

